Command: who [argument]

Without argument shows all current players.

[argument] can be one or more of the following:
    short|newbie|midbie|highbie|wiz|mortal|
    idle|unidle|min (num)|max (num)

If you have colours enabled, some extra info will be indicated by them :
Dark gray - Idle more than 300 seconds
Yellow    - A test character
Cyan      - A reborn player
Magenta   - A dead player (ghost)

Example:
  who mortal unidle min 30
  who short wiz
